// Package bindings holds the Go-side fluent builders for egui2 widgets,
// blocks, and plots — a mix of code generated by egui2gen (the .out.go /
// .gen.go files) and hand-written companions that compose those primitives
// into higher-level surfaces (badges, code views, snarl integration, etc.).
// Consumers typically import this package as `c` and chain calls like
// `c.Button(...).Send()` or `c.Atoms().Text(...).Keep()`.
package bindings
